TronBrowser is an open-source, privacy-first, AI-native web browser built on
Ungoogled Chromium. No telemetry, no ads, no sponsored tabs. It ships an
agent-friendly CLI (tron <url>) and a bring-your-own-keys AI sidebar.

This port installs a launcher that runs the system Chromium with TronBrowser's
privacy flags and the AI sidebar extension.

WWW: https://tronbrowser.dev
